collectionMetadata.name: ACRA Information on Corporate Entities
collectionMetadata.description: This collection provides datasets of registered entities in Singapore. Updated monthly, it is organized into 27 CSV files, one for each letter in the alphabet, and an 'others' dataset. This resource is designed for efficient exploration and analysis by businesses, researchers, and policymakers. Note: A significant number of columns have been removed in consideration of Section 12(2A) of the Companies Act which apply to gazetted companies. This is a more detailed version of the UEN dataset here (https://data.gov.sg/collections/1/view).
